    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="1">
        <title>Cross-View Front Fender-Mounted Mirrors</title>
        <para>The cross-view fender-mounted mirrors (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0900921">Figure 21</hotlnk>) are convex-styled mirrors located on the forward front fender
            sections of the front end assembly. These mirrors allow a cross-view field of vision for the bus operator
            during pick up and discharge of passengers.
        </para>
        <figure id="f0900921" figsize="pg-wide">
